    {
      "key": "79e44a53-eb8d-451b-975b-1b036ab8cd7b",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "**Share Out:** Have students share their work with their peers in some way. Their peers can provide feedback using \"I like...\" and \"What if...\" sentence stems to provide positive constructive feedback. Some options could be:\n- **Class Shareout:** Ask for volunteers and let them share their songs with the whole class, then choose 2-3 students to provide feedback\n- **Pair Networking:** Have students pair up and share their songs and provide feedback, then swap to a new pair\n- **Gallery Walk:** Have students leave their song open on their computer, then walk around and visit other songs. Students carry post-it notes with them and leave feedback on any students they visit."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "79e44a53-eb8d-451b-975b-1b036ab8cd7b",
        "lesson_activity.key": "c49cf448-d8e1-4106-a959-e468b1cac25b"
      }
    },
